<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200915/1b929318245f4de9a6f960451bd0d6f6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>今天荣耀智慧生活微博官宣荣耀游戏本支持一碰回录功能,能够记录下“超神”瞬间,回放极秀操作。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200915/3ff8348f3de44450a2d4497641912fb5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
